snippet.textDisplay: Ukrainian soldiers were trained in France by French gunners to use the 155 mm self-propelled CAESAR gun. These guns are now present in Ukraine and used against Russian troops. The powerful American EXCALIBUR shells compatible with this cannon (NATO standards) were also supplied. These weapons were not destroyed, as announced by Russian-Soviet propaganda.
